    <div xml:id="Aink78">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>katirilai neṭuvēṟ kaṭumāṉ kiḷḷi</l>
<l>matilkol yāṉaiyiṟ kataḻpuneṟi vanta</l>
<l>ciṟaiyaḻi putuppuṉa lāṭuka</l>
<l>memmoṭu koṇmōven tōḷpurai puṇaiyē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

<l>   Let's bathe in the new dam-destroying floods </l> 
<l>   which have come rapidly on their way</l> 
<l>   like one of the fortress-smashing elephants  </l> 
<l>   of Kiḷḷi with his fast horses [and] long spear with its leaf[-shaped] tip [gleaming] like a ray of light.</l> 
<l>   Take hold of [this] raft with us, [this raft] that looks just like our shoulders! </l> 
  
  
  </lg>
